headline: U.S. airlines further amend Taiwan references
summary: Bending to demands from China's aviation regulator, airlines including Delta (NYSE: DAL ), United (NYSE: UAL ), American (NASDAQ: AAL ) and Hawaiian (NASDAQ: HA ) have  amended  their systems to list only Taipei's airport code and city, but not the name Taiwan.
